- bonjourmamie.sh
Prerequisites :
* jp2a
* phosphor

Description : This script download the daily photo of bonjourmadame.fr and convert it to ASCII thanks to lib jp2a.

- rotate.sh
Prerequisites :
* libnotify-dev
* florence
* A touch screen (for me it's a hp 2710p laptop, send me feedback to know if it's work fine with other devices :) )

Description : When you execute it it will rotate your screen (and the 'touch') Counter-Clock Wise and open florence on-screen keyboard, execute once more a and you go back to normal.
